DATA & ATTRIBUTION
Tags, names and descriptions shown by this node come from the AIPaintWorks service,
whose data derives from:
- Tag names, descriptions and co-occurrence statistics from Danbooru
  (https://danbooru.donmai.us).
- Character names and summaries from Bangumi (https://bgm.tv), whose entry and
  character data are licensed under CC BY-SA 3.0
  (https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/); the source is credited as the
  license requires.
- Localized names and some descriptions are automatically generated and translated by
  large language models; they may contain errors or omissions and are for reference
  only — the original English text on Danbooru is authoritative.
This is an unofficial tool, not affiliated with Danbooru or Bangumi.

